===============================================================================

ToyyibPay has been installed!

Next steps:

1. Add your API credentials to your environment variables:

   # For development, add to .env file
   TOYYIBPAY_API_KEY=your-secret-key
   TOYYIBPAY_CATEGORY_CODE=your-category-code
   TOYYIBPAY_SANDBOX=true

   # Or use Rails credentials (Rails 5.2+):
   rails credentials:edit

   And add:
   toyyibpay:
     api_key: your-secret-key
     category_code: your-category-code
     sandbox: true

2. Update config/initializers/toyyibpay.rb if needed

3. Get your API credentials:
   - Production: https://toyyibpay.com
   - Sandbox: https://dev.toyyibpay.com

4. Start using ToyyibPay in your Rails app:

   # Create a bill
   bill = ToyyibPay.bills.create(
     billName: "Invoice #001",
     billDescription: "Payment for services",
     billPriceSetting: "0",
     billPayorInfo: "1",
     billAmount: "10000",
     billPaymentChannel: "0"
   )

   # Get payment URL
   payment_url = ToyyibPay.bills.payment_url(bill[0]["BillCode"])

For more information, visit:
https://github.com/revolutionstage/toyyibpay-rails

===============================================================================
